snippet.title: Escape from Bunker. VR Roomscale Game. Quest 2\Pro. Trailer V2
snippet.description:
Oculus Store:
https://www.oculus.com/experiences/quest/5458048390976704/

This is a game with a fascinating story, stunning graphics and a quest-room style atmosphere. The peculiarity of the game is moving using a real space of 4 by 3 meters. This gives a unique and unrepeatable immersion in the gameplay!
You can try to turn your room into a Real Adventure!
VERSION 2 IS OUT! 6 MORE NEW ROOMS ADDED!!! LOTS OF NEW GAME CONTENT!
